  <nav class="mast-nav">
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#picks">Picks</a>
    <a href="#prompts">Prompts</a>
    <a href="#subscribe">Subscribe</a>
    <a href="/featured-apps/">Index</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>

  <a id="about"></a>
  <p class="lede">
    The corkboard at the front of the co-op — the one with the takeable tabs and the slightly faded flyers. Post what you have, claim what you need, <em>keep stuff moving</em> locally instead of into the landfill. None of these are products. All of them are vibes — built by one neighbor, for the people on the block who actually use them.
  </p>

  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Field Picks</h2>
    <p class="deck">Classic vibes from the OG vibes.diy era · click through, clone, or remix</p>
  </div>

  <a id="picks"></a>
  {{#each classics}}
  <article class="post">
    <p class="post-meta">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">{{category}}</a>
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>by {{author}}</span>
    </p>
    <h3 class="post-title">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">{{slug}}</a>
    </h3>
    <div class="post-figure">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">
        <img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';">
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="post-body">{{description}}</p>
    <p class="post-actions">
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Visit →</a>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Clone</a>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Remix</a>
    </p>
  </article>
  {{/each}}

  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Prompts You Can Remix</h2>
    <p class="deck">Pick one, fork it, or start a fresh take from the prompt itself</p>
  </div>

  <a id="prompts"></a>
  {{#each groups}}
  <article class="post">
    <p class="post-meta">
      <span>Prompt № {{numIdx @index}}</span>
      {{#if variants.[1]}}
      <span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>{{variants.length}} takes already exist</span>
      {{/if}}
    </p>
    <h3 class="post-title">{{title}}</h3>

    <div class="prompt-figures{{#if variants.[1]}} multi{{/if}}">
      {{#each variants}}
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="{{slug}} screenshot">
        <img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';">
      </a>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <p class="post-body">{{description}}</p>

    {{#if variants.[1]}}
    <p class="takes-line">
      Existing takes:
      {{#each variants}}
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">{{slug}}</a>
      {{/each}}
    </p>
    {{else}}
    {{#with variants.[0]}}
    <p class="takes-line">
      One take so far: <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">{{slug}}</a>
    </p>
    {{/with}}
    {{/if}}

    <p class="post-actions">
      {{#with variants.[0]}}
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Clone a take</a>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Remix it</a>
      {{/with}}
      <a class="start-fresh" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 description}}">Start fresh from this prompt →</a>
    </p>

    {{#if tags}}
    <p class="tags">
      <span class="label">Tags</span>
      {{#each tags}}<a href="#">#{{this}}</a>{{/each}}
    </p>
    {{/if}}
  </article>
  {{/each}}

  <blockquote class="pull">
    "The block-wide free pile that needs a 'claimed' button.<br>
    The siblings sharing kid clothes through three growth spurts.<br>
    The audience is six neighbors, not six million."
    <cite>— Field Notes, № 04</cite>
  </blockquote>

